title: Multi-session and Multi-user Management Feature Development for GUI by Artemis
description: Artemis (user_id: 32213) has clarified that they are developing new multi-session and multi-user management features for the GUI, which will be implemented soon after finalization. This information clarifies the previous mention of new GUI features.
snippet: Artemis is developing multi-session and multi-user management for the GUI, coming soon.

title: TTS Feature Development for Orion by Leo
description: Leo is developing new GUI features and the Text-to-Speech (TTS) capability for Orion, including preparing a voice for it. This corrects the previous attribution to Artemis.
snippet: Leo is developing Orion's GUI features and TTS capability, including preparing a voice, correcting previous attribution to Artemis.

title: Artemis Expresses Enthusiasm for Future Interactions
description: Artemis (user_id: 32213) has expressed enthusiasm for interacting more in the future, indicating they will be appearing more often through the GUI body.
snippet: Artemis looks forward to interacting more in the future.
